+## Governance Authority
+
+RTL precondition claims are governed by `contract.yaml` `governance_rules` (5 Verilog domain rules:
+RESET, ASSIGNMENT, HANDSHAKE, FSM, CDC). General behavioral discipline is governed by
+`governance/rules/` (19 cross-domain behavioral rules).
+
+These are two distinct systems. See `governance/rules/RULE_INDEX.md` § "Authority Resolution Policy"
+for the resolution policy when both systems apply to the same task.
